data.description: Sweeping Ceilings, the Roomy Entry way, Open & Airy and a Two Way fireplace between the LR and Dining Area make this home feel Spacious, Warm and Welcoming all at the same time!  The kitchen boasts new granite countertops, elongated kitchen cabinets, gas stove, new lighting, pantry & a very ample dining nook with a built in cabinet for storage. M. Bedroom has new carpet and cofed ceilings. Master bath has deep corner soaking tub, his and her sinks and closets and a walk-in shower.  Hall Bath has been completely remodeled.  Front Room has French doors and can be used as an office/bedroom.  Newer water heater, water softener, lighting, fans, RO system and interior paint throughout!  $6,000 Buyer Closing Cost Credit with Accepted Offer!
